  <name>BingTray</name>
  <summary>Bing Wallpaper Manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A cross-platform wallpaper manager that downloads and manages Bing's weekly wallpapers.
      Bing wallpapers are updated weekly sets of 8 images.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download wallpapers from multiple Bing markets</li>
      <li>Automatic wallpaper rotation</li>
      <li>Favorite wallpapers management</li>
      <li>Blacklist unwanted wallpapers</li>
      <li>System tray integration</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
